04:01.785 --> 04:03.322
That didn't go well.

04:03.466 --> 04:05.187
Eh, too many people have died.

04:05.635 --> 04:07.073
It's a PR nightmare.

04:07.703 --> 04:08.769
Got to blame someone.

04:08.885 --> 04:10.109
Agent Parker!

04:10.272 --> 04:11.479
I just heard from Franklin.

04:13.181 --> 04:14.464
Will you excuse us?

04:16.841 --> 04:18.244
I'll wait in the car.

04:21.194 --> 04:22.580
Am I out?

04:22.752 --> 04:24.449
I know they're discussing it.
Just tell me.

04:24.563 --> 04:27.559
No, but they are taking the
operation control to DC.

04:27.903 --> 04:29.299
Where does that leave me?

04:30.405 --> 04:33.629
Everyone recognizes that Ryan
Hardy's integral to all this,

04:33.765 --> 04:35.303
but he's a wild card.

04:35.430 --> 04:37.829
They want you to stay
on, hold his hand.

04:38.436 --> 04:39.714
You'll keep your taskforce here

04:39.862 --> 04:41.911
and continue to report to me.

04:44.658 --> 04:46.268
Understood.

